    "Face download count for the paper and dataset, dated September 2023.",
    "This acts as an estimate of community use, and is commonly used as precedence to decide on the risk level for using these datasets.",
    "The DPExplorer displays the collected data in a format accessible to developers by applying different aggregation, specialized filtering and tallying steps to obtain data summary statistics and overviews.",
